# Schedule Terminology

Use consistent terminology to avoid confusion:

- **Trainer availability block** — A block of time when a trainer is available (from `trainer_availability`). These are **bookable**; PT sessions are booked within them. Do NOT use "block slot" or bare "block" when referring to these.

- **Blocked-off time** / **unavailable** — Time intentionally blocked off (from `unavailable_blocks`), e.g. doctor's appointment. These are **not bookable**. Use "blocked-off time" in user-facing text when removing or describing these.
